Source: Farm Engineering
Author: RIDDOLLS
Vol / Page: 425
Edition:
Quote: It [a flood-gate] will act as a stock block during dry periods, will open by swinging downstream during floods, and return to its normal position afterwards, providing no logs or boulders have lodged under it.
